  "body_html": "<p>For the vanilla girls that love every kind of vanilla.</p>\n<p>The Trio Obsession bundle includes Vanille, Fluffy Mallow, and Sundae — all in 50ml sizes. Each fragrance brings a different vanilla personality, giving you the perfect scent for every mood. From the spicy, mature, and elegant vanilla, to the playful fresh one, all the way to the rich gourmand edible sweetness — this bundle has it all.</p>\n<p>Three vanillas, three different vibes, one obsession.</p>",
